text: Robert "Robin" Henry Alexander Eames, Baron Eames, (born 27 April 1936), is an Anglican bishop. He served as Primate of All Ireland and Archbishop of Armagh from 1986 to 2006. ==References== Category:1936 births Category:Living people Category:Anglican archbishops Category:Anglican priests Category:British Anglicans Category:Northern Irish Protestants Category:People from Belfast
